Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.58,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不行没勇气。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:21.26,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.27,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:25.56,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这个画面是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.26,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,怎么回到上个画面？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.38,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,教你用智能手机？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:50.67,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,都不知道你还在用翻盖机。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.58,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦是的。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:56.48,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,真像你。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.56,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,像我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.23,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,拜托了田山老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.62,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,行我教你。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:05.56,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,真的？谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.01,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,那你有什么搞不定的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.19,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:14.33,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,说出来丢人\N我连基本操作都不会。
