Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:20.59,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.08,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,基本操作是吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.86,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,好，我教你有用的功能。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.08,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,拜托了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:32.84,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,从最基础的开始。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:37.30,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,回主屏幕你肯定懂\N跳过。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:40.58,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那个能不能也教一下……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:48.20,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,智能手机用滑动输入。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:52.31,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,按屏幕上的键然后\N咻地滑到要输入的字母。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.77,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,咻？好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:55.48,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs12\c&H636363&\frz-12.38\pos(297,276.5)}ka
