Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.95,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(101,67)\fs12\c&H636363&\frz349\pos(294,291.5)}ko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:57.37,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,来打「ko」。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:58.19,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,咻……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.74,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(66,1)\fs14\c&H5B5B5B&\frz-12.38\pos(257,77)}Ka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:00.74,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等不——！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.49,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这不是我要的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.65,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,换种输入法？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.41,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好的拜托了。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:17.76,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对了我想试试在手机上看报纸。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.56,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,可以啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.33,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:25.76,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,先打开应用商店安装报纸的App。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:29.44,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,主屏幕上应该能找到。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:33.52,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,但要注册账号才能用。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:36.53,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,注册完登录。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.42,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,再安装报纸的App。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:41.64,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,那个也得注册账号。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.15,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(226,1)\bord2\fs12\c&H2C2D31&\3c&H979797&\frz13.33\fax-0.4\pos(569,303)}Manual
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:50.87,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,算了，我帮你装。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.19,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对不起谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.46,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,145)\fax0.1\fs10\fnTimes New Roman\c&H9A9A9A&\frz0.42\pos(242.5,52)}EIHO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:02.78,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐最好了\N这下应该能像旧手机一样用了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:10.43,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,慢慢用就习惯了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:15.14,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,抱歉还能再问件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.19,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:19.80,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,能把字体调大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.04,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,啥……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.45,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:27.97,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你连智能手机都不会用\N怎么知道能调字体？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:30.66,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,翻盖机也能调啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.03,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,有、有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.64,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:44.22,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,改那个设置很麻烦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.87,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,帮你弄倒是没问题……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.78,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,但你不准不戴老花镜。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.34,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.05,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,给我我帮你调。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:37.02,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,对了佐佐木先生\N为了庆祝你加入智能手机一族。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.85,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我把山田小姐的号码给你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.78,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不不不不用了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.03,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,别这样田山小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:48.08,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,侵犯隐私而且……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.06,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那可是山田小姐啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:50.91,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,迟了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.56,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,已经存进去了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:57.92,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你怎么能……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.82,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.77,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,开玩笑的。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:04.94,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.68,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,好了搞定了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.76,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.91,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,好了现在好读多了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.47,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:14.03,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等不——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.85,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,哎呀好吓人。
