Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.99,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.79,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好了今天有什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.49,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,他不知道我偷拍了一张。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:32.55,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好了该上班了。
